Class CharSequenceValueConverter

java.lang.Object
io.netty.handler.codec.CharSequenceValueConverter
All Implemented Interfaces:
ValueConverter<CharSequence>
public class CharSequenceValueConverter extends Object implements ValueConverter<CharSequence>
Converts to/from native types, general Object, and CharSequences.
